                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">American Consul at Ciudad Juárez</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-04-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 10, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Press reports that rebels have taken from George Drake official despatches which
                    he was carrying to El Paso for Consul at Chihuahua. Investigate, and, if true,
                    discreetly but vigorously endeavor to secure despatches.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Huntington Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
